OL,5,G```FFIDE WORLD CHAMPIONSHIPG```````````
OL,7,GCongratulations to Nigel Short!  Yet   
OL,8,Gan other convinving display from the   
OL,9,G1993 World Championship Challenger sees
OL,10,Ghim marching through to the semi-finals
OL,11,Galong with Anand.                      
OL,13,FJoint-British champion, Mickey Adams   
OL,14,Fhad to perform an escape act of Houdini
OL,15,Fpromortions, drawing in 92 moves, to   
OL,16,Ftake his match with Van Wely into the  
OL,17,Ffirst 25 min play-off.                 
OL,19,FAt stake? A small matter of $192,000!  
