OL,5,G```FEDINBURGH CHALLENGEG`````````````` 
OL,7,GScotland's leading player IM Jonathan  
OL,8,GRowson has won the #5,000 Edinburgh    
OL,9,GChallenge against IM Tiger Hillarp-    
OL,10,GPersson, with one game to spare.       
OL,12,FThe match, running alongside the 2nd   
OL,13,FCaledonian Masters, at the Capital Moat
OL,14,FHouse, Edinburgh, saw Rowson picking up
OL,15,F#3,500 as winner.  He's now won #8,500 
OL,16,Fin the past year in challenge matches! 
OL,18,FIM J Rowson         B1 1B0B1B1B\ C4\   
OL,19,FIM T Hillarp-PerssonB0 0B1B0B0 \ C1\   
