OL,5,G```FEUROPEAN TEAM CHAMPIONSHIP 1999G```
OL,7,GThe BCF have announced that the venue  
OL,8,Gfor the 1999 European Team Ch, to be   
OL,9,Gheld 3-11 July 1999, will be the       
OL,10,GRiviera Centre, Torquay.               
OL,11,G                                       
OL,12,FThe announcement comes after the dual  
OL,13,Fsuccess of the English teams at the    
OL,14,F1997 Team Ch, where the men's team     
OL,15,Flifted the gold and the women's the    
OL,16,Fbronze.                                
OL,17,F                                       
OL,18,FIt's anticipated that over 300 top     
OL,19,Fplayers from 40 countries will compete.
