OL,5,G```FRICHMOND RAPIDPLAYG``````````````` 
OL,7,C7 December, White House Comm Assoc.    
OL,8,GIM Peter Large was the winner of this  
OL,9,Gpopular tournament. Scoring 5\/6, he   
OL,10,Gcame ahead of a strong field including 
OL,11,GIM Danny Kopec (USA) and WGM Wang Pin  
OL,12,G(Chn).                                 
OL,14,FA 180 performance came from the little 
OL,15,Fman with the big name in chess, Murugan
OL,16,FThiruchelvam of Richmond Jnrs. Just 4  
OL,17,Fdays shy of his ninth birthday, he     
OL,18,Fproduces a result ahead of Short, Adams
OL,19,Fand McShane at a similar age.          
